# Running Runner as Background Service

Manual runner stops after terminal closes.

Better approach:

Run as Linux service.

---

# Install Service

```bash id="jlwmf3"
sudo ./svc.sh install
```

---

# Start Service

```bash id="jlwm7o"
sudo ./svc.sh start
```

---

# Check Service Status

```bash id="jlwm1v"
sudo ./svc.sh status
```

